HEADWORD: Expiratory
<hw>Ex*pir"a*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or employed in, the expiration
or emission of air from the lungs; <as>as, the <ex>expiratory</ex>
muscles</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

